description: Ten Tails is on the brink of its final transformation and begins to form a massive Tailed Beast Bomb.
title: Something to Fill the Hole

description: Sakura focuses on her healing skills while Naruto and Sasuke aim for Ten Tails. Meanwhile, the five Kage battling Madara have sustained critical injuries.
title: The New Three-Way Deadlock

description: Kakashi holds on to the hope that Obito can return to being the young man that he remembers. But Obito has abandoned the present as well as the memories of his friends and will not try to stop the Infinite Tsukuyomi.
title: Kakashi vs. Obito

description: Part 1 of a special two-part extra edition! The townspeople are going about their daily business on the streets of the Leaf Village when someone suddenly appears and starts sending them flying!

input: The Directive to Take the Nine-Tails!

title: The Directive to Take the Nine-Tails!

description: Minato is filled with regret during his confrontation with Obito.
title: The Day Naruto Was Born

description: Hashirama, Tobirama, Hiruzen, the Five Kage, Orochimaru and every shinobi on the battlefield join together to cut down the Divine Tree!
title: Pursuing Hope

description: Working in sync, Naruto and Sasuke prepare to attack in the same way Madara once did, cloaking Kurama in Susano'o's robes.
title: A Heart Filled With Comrades

description: Obito's turned every shinobi against him and intends on ending the world. Naruto then asserts that Obito is merely abandoning everything and running away.
title: Obito Uchiha

description: Pressed by Naruto, Obito remembers the time he, Kakashi, and Rin teamed up for the Chunin Exam and when he promised Rin that he would become Hokage.
title: I'm Always Watching

description: Naruto's power of persuasion moves Obito's heart. Due to the influence of the Ten Tails, visions of himself and Rin from the past appear in the inner realm and play havoc with Obito's emotions.
title: The Promise That Was Kept

description: Naruto and the Allied Shinobi Forces successfully extract the Tailed Beasts from Obito. Only Madara remains, and Naruto heads out to tackle this foe.
title: Madara Uchiha Rises

description: The Tailed Beasts and the Allied Shinobi Forces shift their focus onto their greatest foe, Madara Uchiha.
title: My First Friend

description: Hanabi adores her sister Hinata, who struggles to become a worthy successor to the Hyuga Clan.
title: The Adored Elder Sister

description: When Hinata is labeled unfit as a successor, Hanabi's heart becomes bound to her destiny.
title: Hanabi's Decision

description: Naruto loses Kurama during his battle against Madara and is near death. As Tsunade and the other Leaf Village shinobi watch in fear, they are reminded that Naruto has always been their symbol of hope, even when he was not with them…
title: The New Chunin Exams

description: The Second Exam finally begins! To pass this stage, each team must take possession of both the Heaven and Earth scrolls and make it to the designated site in the center of the Demon Desert within 72 hours.
title: Demon Desert Survival

description: Lee challenges Shira to a battle between taijutsu users!  Lee is pushed into using his Eight Inner Gates, but he is unable to release the First Gate!
title: The Ultimate

description: As fighting breaks out for the scrolls, Tenten feels an intense rivalry with Ajisai, who also specializes in Transportation Ninjutsu.
title: Tenten's Troubles

description: Kiba and his team are in pursuit of Hidden Grass Ninja who have stolen their scroll.
title: Unwavering Gutsiness

description: Witnessing Ajisai's proficiency with the Summoning Jutsu, Tenten recalls her training with Guy.
title: The Imprisoned Pair

description: Ino, Sakura and Choji trudge across the desert without any provisions. Ino and Sakura start arguing when a giant scorpion attacks.
title: The Place Where I Belong

description: As Ino and her team head toward an oasis, they are attacked by a team of Sand Shinobi comprised of Ameno, Shishio, and Kouji.
title: The Yamanaka Clan: Secret Ninjutsu

description: Sakura and her team continue their trek across the desert towards the goal. When they stop to rest, they encounter a puppet manipulated by a rival team from the Sand.
title: The Cursed Puppet

description: Sakura realizes that she has trained with Lady Tsunade and regains her confidence that she can protect Ino and Choji from the Sand Shinobi.
title: Their Backs

description: The Sand Jonin Fugi sneaks into the Demon Desert and creates a massive sandstorm in order to assassinate Gaara, the Fifth Kazekage.

input: The Hidden Plot Set Into Motion

title: The Hidden Plot Set Into Motion

description: Neji and the team come across Matsuri collapsed in the desert and find out that Gaara is in danger.
title: Neji's Judgment

description: Fuu senses that Gaara is in danger and abandons the Chunin Exams to help save him.
title: The Targeted Tailed Beast

description: Gaara confronts Fugi, the mastermind behind the assassination attempt on his life.
title: Hopes Entrusted to the Future

description: Kakashi has changed for the worse, and Obito doesn't know why. He runs into Kakashi and tries to talk to him, but Kakashi gives him the cold shoulder.
title: The Formation of Team Minato

description: Madara has transformed into the Jinchuriki of the Ten Tails and appears before Kakashi.
title: The Two Mangekyo

description: Naruto is on the verge of dying. Sakura desperately tries to save him, but Naruto's heart gives out.
title: On the Brink of Death

description: Obito doesn't understand Kakashi's way of thinking, but he finally learns why Kakashi prioritized his mission first at Kannabi Bridge.
title: You'll Be My Backup

description: Guy releases his Eight Inner Gates against Madara, but the Seventh Gate of Shock does not work against him!

input: The Blue Beast vs. Six Paths Madara
Blue Beast vs. Six Paths Madara

title: The Blue Beast vs. Six Paths Madara
